JD - 8 :

Requisites:
· Candidate should have relevant experience of 4 to 5 years in the field of public relations.
· In-depth understanding and being well-networked with relevant feature media and bloggers
· Has expertise in creating content and business communication that builds and bolsters strong and sophisticated brand identities.
· Strong communication skills, both verbal and written.

Responsibilities
1. Client Servicing: Establishing and nurturing relationships with respective clients
· Planning, developing, and implementing PR strategies for brands within the industry of choice.
· Driving high-impact news coverage (stories, interviews, and other formats)

2. Strong media relations and Influencer Marketing
· Build, maintain, and enhance new or existing relationships with media personnel (journalists)
· Generating opportunities in media for various client coverage, stories, media dialogues, and interviews.

3. Content Writing: Master of Communication
· Create content or a business communiqué that builds and bolsters strong and sophisticated brand identities.

